der of Merit of the Italian Republic]] (Cavaliere di Gran Croce Ordine al Merito della Repubblica Italiana).<ref name=\"Quirinale\" />\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist\n| refs =\n\n<ref name=\"Bayreuth\">{{cite web\n| url = https://www.bayreuther-festspiele.de/en/festspiele/news/2020/death-of-long-time-former-choir-director-prof-norbert-balatsch/\n| title = Death of long-time former choir director Prof. Norbert Balatsch\n| website = [[Bayreuth Festival]]\n| date = 8 May 2020\n| accessdate = 8 May 2020\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Bayreuth Ehrenring\">{{cite web\n| url = https://www.bayreuth.de/rathaus-buergerservice/stadtverwaltung/ehrungen-auszeichnungen/goldener-ehrenring/\n| title = Goldener Ehrenring\n| website = [[Bayreuth]]\n| date = 8 May 2020\n| accessdate = 8 May 2020\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Grammy\">{{cite web\n| url = https://www.grammy.com/grammys/artists/norbert-balatsch\n| title = Artist / Norbert Balatsch\n| website = [[Grammy Awards]]\n| date = 2020\n| accessdate = 8 May 2020\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Maazel\">{{cite web\n| url = http://www.santacecilia.it/file_gallery/MAESTRO_LORIN_MAAZEL_-_SANTA_CECILIA.pdf\n| title = Maestro Lorin Maazel / Orchestra e Coro dell\u2019Accademia Nazionale di Santa Cecilia\n| website = santacecilia.it\n| date = \n| accessdate = 8 May 2020\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ORF\">{{cite web\n| url = https://orf.at/stories/3164802/\n| title = Ehemaliger Staatsopernchordirektor Balatsch ist tot\n| website = [[ORF]]\n| date = 7 May 2020\n| language = de\n| accessdate = 8 May 2020\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Philharmonia\">{{cite web\n| url = https://www.guildmusic.com/shop/wbc.php?tpl=artistdruck.html&pid=13842\n| title = Biography of The Philharmonia Chorus\n| website = guildmusic.com\n| date = 2020\n| accessdate = 8 May 2020\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Quirinale\">{{cite web\n| url = https://archivio.quirinale.it/aspr/comunicati/PRESSRELEASE-001-009787/presidente/giorgio-napolitano/il-presidente-napolitano-ha-ricevuto-maestro-norbert-balatsc